text: Marco Antonio Martinez Dabdoub is a Mexican politician. He is the mayor of the city of Nogales, Sonora, and a member of the National Action Party. ==See also== * List of Mexican people ==Sources== * Luis Alatorre, Luis; Holley, Denise (October 16, 2008). "Mayor of Nogales, Sonora, Defends City In Wake of U.S. Travel Alert". Nogales International.
